Package: Romney
Type: Package
Title: Classical Cultural Consensus Analysis in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Werner", family = "Hertzog", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "werner.hertzog@isek.uzh.ch")
Description: Tools for classical cultural consensus analysis including
    formal, informal, and covariance agreement models, UCINET-aligned
    minimum-residual factor extraction, competence estimation, and
    answer-key estimation. Implements the classical framework of
    Romney, Weller, and Batchelder (1986)
    <doi:10.1525/aa.1986.88.2.02a00020>, Romney, Batchelder, and
    Weller (1987) <doi:10.1177/000276487031002003>, and Weller (2007)
    <doi:10.1177/1525822X07303502>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    psych,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Author: Werner Hertzog [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Werner Hertzog <werner.hertzog@isek.uzh.ch>
URL: https://github.com/wernerhertzog/Romney
BugReports: https://github.com/wernerhertzog/Romney/issues
